data.description: This remarkable residence situated in Cureton Woods is a must-see gem! Step inside this capacious, rarely available five-bedroom home nestled on a sizable corner lot. The house boasts an inviting open-concept layout with beautiful hardwood flooring throughout the main level, a cozy fireplace in the family room, and a dedicated office/den space. The main level conveniently includes a bedroom and full bathroom, perfect for accommodating guests. The kitchen features a gas oven/stovetop, an island, and a spacious pantry. The oversized primary suite offers a tray ceiling and a separate sitting area complete with a fireplace, creating a tranquil retreat for relaxation. The primary bathroom features upgraded flooring, a double vanity, a separate shower and tub, and an exceptionally spacious walk-in closet. The upstairs guest bedrooms are generously proportioned, offering ample space for all. The expansive, fenced backyard provides endless possibilities. With easy access to I-20, East-West Connector, shopping, and dining, this home offers exceptional value, ensuring immediate equity for the savvy buyer.
